<item>
            <title>[HIVE-11498] HIVE Authorization v2 should not check permission for dummy entity</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-11498</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The queries like &lt;tt&gt;SELECT 1+1;&lt;/tt&gt;, The target table and database will set to &lt;tt&gt;_dummy_database&lt;/tt&gt; &lt;tt&gt;_dummy_table&lt;/tt&gt;, authorization should skip these kinds of databases or tables.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For authz v1. it has skip them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;eg1. &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/master/ql/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/ql/Driver.java#L600&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Source code at github&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;for (WriteEntity write : outputs) {
        if (write.isDummy() || write.isPathType()) {
          continue;
        }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;eg2. &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/master/ql/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/ql/Driver.java#L633&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Source code at github&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;for (ReadEntity read : inputs) {
        if (read.isDummy() || read.isPathType()) {
          continue;
        }
       ...
        }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch will fix authz v2.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
